thread.title: Multiple shots fired at car on I-225 early Friday morning
thread.title_full: Multiple shots fired at car on I-225 early Friday morning - The Denver Post

author: Elizabeth Hernandez
title: Multiple shots fired at car on I-225 early Friday morning
text:
The Aurora Police Department is investigating after someone in a vehicle on Interstate 225 shot at another commuter early Friday morning, officials said.
A white sedan and a black sedan were southbound on I-225 from East Iliff Avenue around 3 a.m. when a person in the black sedan shot multiple rounds at the white sedan, according to Aurora police spokeswoman Diana Cooley.
The occupants of the vehicles do not appear to know each other and no one was injured in the incident, Cooley said.
The white vehicle was towed for evidence.
This is a developing story that will be updated as more information becomes available.
